layout.content:
// The Problem
Wearing my video technician and AV system design hat, I often juggled disconnected tools for calibration, analysis, and asset generation when planning and setting up testing on a project. Calculating pixel densities, generating test patterns, and verifying signal flows usually required switching between multiple single-purpose apps, copying and pasting assets and values between each one.

// My Solution
'OpKit Patchbay' is a node based workflow toolkit for the web. Built on 'React Flow', it allows users to chain together functional nodes; Generators, Analysers, and Calibration tools into custom saveable and sharable workflows.
